<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> OBLIGATIONS OF THE SELLER</span></h3>
<ol style="text-align: justify;">
	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Seller shall maintain records of all the Products purchased by the Buyers through the Platform, all returns, refunds, etc., as may be required for audit and regulatory purposes and for the Platformâ€™s customer service purposes.</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">During the Term, Seller shall appoint a representative, who shall be Paytmâ€™s point of contact for any and all matters related to this Agreement, including all sales and delivery related matters.</span></li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">III. Seller shall be solely responsible and liable for any complaints and queries of Buyers with respect to the Products, delayed delivery or non-delivery of the Products purchased or any complaints with respect to the quality or quantity of the Products delivered.</span></p>

<ol style="text-align: justify;">
